{"id":186892,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011105/","date":"2011-10-07T19:30:52Z","modified":"2011-10-07T19:30:52Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/10/5","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><span> </span><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/asia-pacific/a-chinese-resident-who-doesnt-know-liu-xiaobo-blame-the-river-crabs/article2191625/?utm_medium=Feeds%3A%20RSS%2FAtom&#038;utm_source=Asia-Pacific&#038;utm_content=2191625\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国居民不知道刘晓波是谁？这要怪“河蟹”</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——由于河蟹们的努力，像刘晓波和艾未未这样的名字对绝大多数中国人来说都是陌生的。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/joelkotkin/2011/10/04/are-we-headed-for-chinas-fat-years/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">我们是否面临着《盛世・中国》的时代？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——陈冠中小说中的场面似乎已经出现，但是西方应看到自身的优势，不可妄自菲薄</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/06/world/asia/06iht-letter06.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">达赖喇嘛紧紧把握住继承人的选择权</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他最近公布了关于转世问题的一些思考，其基本点就是：中国无权决定他的继承人。对此中国当然不同意。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/10/05/petty-officials/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的底层官员</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——地位不高但手里有权的官僚最容易滥用权力。从城管到银行职员，这样的例子比比皆是。有人认为是中国的文化造就了这一现象，但作者不同意。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《旺报》（台湾）：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wantchinatimes.com/news-subclass-cnt.aspx?id=20111003000018&#038;cid=1501&#038;MainCatID=0\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一场革命，两种解释</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——辛亥革命</span></span><span><span>100</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年将至，台湾和大陆对这场革命的解读有所区别。前者强调中华民国的成立，后者强调中国人民反抗帝制</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>ABC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新闻：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://abclocal.go.com/wls/story?section=news/local&#038;id=8378972\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">摩托罗拉商业间谍案的新细节</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——检方指控华裔雇员下载敏感技术文件准备交给在中国的新雇主和中国军方。该雇员在机场离境时被截下。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/oct/05/russia-arrests-chinese-translator-spying\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">俄国拘捕</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一名</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国间谍</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在普京访华前夕，俄起诉了一名去年底被拘捕的试图获取敏感导弹技术的中国间谍。嫌疑人是中国官方代表团的一名翻译。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《财富》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2011/10/04/alibaba-yahoo-jack-ma/?section=magazines_fortune\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">阿里巴巴的马云不是双重间谍</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——很多人对阿里巴巴打算购买雅虎感到不安，但作者认为他们的批评是错误的。美国需要中国投资购买除了国债以外的东西</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/10/05/patriotic-chinese-hacking-group-reboots/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国爱国主义黑客组织东山再起</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——曾经发起对美国网络攻击的“中国红客联盟”，在沉寂数年后再度出现。但是组织者称今后将进行合法活动</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/checkpoint-washington/post/congressman-lambasts-chinese-cyber-espionage/2011/10/04/gIQA5SM7KL_blog.html?wprss=checkpoint-washington\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国众议员猛烈抨击中国的网络间谍行为</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——众议院情报委员会主席称中国政府利用网络盗窃商业信息和知识产权。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://thecable.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2011/10/04/has_the_obama_administration_made_a_decision_on_selling_taiwan_new_planes_or_not\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">奥巴马当局到底决定了向台湾出售新飞机没有？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——上月底美国宣布向台湾出售</span></span><span><span>F-16A/B</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，但并没有说不出售新型的</span></span><span><span>F-16C/D</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》社论：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/10/05/opinion/the-wrong-way-to-deal-with-china.html?_r=2&#038;emc=tnt&#038;tntemail1=y\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">与中国打交道的错误方式</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的确是在操纵汇率，但参议院起草的惩罚中国的议案，最终伤害的可能还是美国自身。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/janetcarmosky/2011/10/05/theus_china_and_jobs/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国，中国和就业：与汇率无关</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——指责中国操纵汇率的议案只是一个心理安慰，并不能解决美国就业问题的根本原因</span></span><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国节奏博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thechinabeat.org/?p=3845\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">关于鸦片战争的记忆：中印对比</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——对于中国人来说，鸦片战争开启了百年耻辱。而印度人则多少为自己当年的角色感到内疚，希望忘记这场战争。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/asean-beat/2011/10/05/burma-bamboozles-china/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">缅甸把中国搞晕了</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——很多人都在问：缅甸的变化是“民选”文职政府的真心所为呢，还是只不过是恶狼披上一件新羊皮？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《基督教科学箴言报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/World/terrorism-security/2011/1005/A-cheap-ruse-US-slams-Russia-and-China-for-vetoing-UN-resolution-on-Syria?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+feeds%2Fworld+%28Christian+Science+Monitor+%7C+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国谴责中俄在叙利亚问题上投反对票，称其为“廉价的把戏”</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/politics/2011/oct/05/hague-russia-china-siding-syria\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">英外长指责俄中与叙利亚的“野蛮政权站在一起”</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——黑格称中俄投反对票是没有站在人民的一边，也是极大的错误。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/10/04/afghanistan_oil_china_great_game\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么五角大楼</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">把</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">阿富汗的财富交给中国？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中石油将获得阿富汗几个油田的开采权。令人震惊的是，美国国防部的政策促成了这一结果。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东亚论坛：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eastasiaforum.org/2011/10/05/does-us-china-strategic-cooperation-have-to-be-so-hard/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中美战略合作关系一定要这么难实现吗？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中美在中国周边国家的问题上进行合作的历史其实很长，目前的僵局不是因为双方缺乏共同利益，作者提出了几种解决途径。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/10/05/us-china-yuan-idUSTRE79411620111005?feedType=RSS&#038;feedName=Yuan&#038;virtualBrandChannel=11721&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+reuters%2FUSyuanNews+%28News+%2F+US+%2F+YUAN+GCA%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人民币坚挺对美国意外着什么？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——它可以使美国的赤字减少</span></span><span><span>1/3</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">并为美国创造一定的就业机会，但它也可能导致贸易战，并使全球经济陷入衰退</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/oct/05/malcolm-turnbull-china-india-climate\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中印将成为阻止全球变暖的领袖</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“气候变化先行者”称中印看到了气候变暖带来的恶果，因此会大力投入。而怀疑科学的美国和其他国家将落在后面</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnbc.com/id/44752529\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的创新要感谢美国的教育</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——过去</span></span><span><span>30</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年里有</span></span><span><span>100</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万中国人到海外读书，其中回国的不到</span></span><span><span>30</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万。如果中国的教育体制不改革，创新就不太可能发生。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国外人博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chinabystander.wordpress.com/2011/10/05/hot-springs-eternal-china-iceland-and-geothermal-energy/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">永远的温泉：中国，冰岛和地热能源</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——地热发电在中国现有能源供应中的地位微乎其微，但中国正与冰岛合作，学习对方的技术来提升地热利用率</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5ieBX2VxDGU4FPD793xmhHySwbtpg?docId=CNG.1b4173c91859fa8854e49ff82ceb4294.431\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国</span>iPhone 5<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大削价</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——苹果发布会之后，山寨</span></span><span><span>iPhone 5</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">出现跳水价，只要</span></span><span><span>200</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">元就可以从淘宝上买到了。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>Fox News: <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.q13fox.com/news/la-fi-china-fake-phones-20111004,0,5566953.story\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">山寨手机在中国渐渐失去魅力</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——高端手机价格一路下滑，使得山寨品牌的市场越来越小</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">我看中国：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://ilookchina.net/2010/01/28/my-experience-as-an-inmate-in-a-chinese-jail-viewed-as-single-page/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">我在中国蹲监狱的经历</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——到上海找工作的美国青年因签证过期被关了</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">天，出来后被遣送回国。这是他写的狱中见闻。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-6727009796782723534?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[9041,8819,8840]}